org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream

Class SplitDataStream<OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream.SplitDataStream<OUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    OUT - The type of the output.

    public class SplitDataStream<OUT>
extends Object
    The SplitDataStream represents an operator that has been split using an OutputSelector. Named outputs can be selected using the select(java.lang.String...) function.
